BT /F2 10 Tf 54 606 Td (Displayed field: Amount Paid) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 54 582 Td (  - Formula: `sum\(InvoicePayment.amount_applied for invoice\)`) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 54 570 Td (  - Source: `invoices/models.py:Invoice.get_amount_paid`) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 54 558 Td (  - Explanation: Adds all payment allocations attached to that invoice.) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 54 546 Td (  - Example: Allocations are KES 5,000 and KES 2,000. Amount paid = `5,000 + 2,000 = 7,000`.) Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 54 526 Td (Displayed field: Balance Due / Remaining Balance) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 54 502 Td (  - Formula: `invoice.amount - invoice.get_amount_paid\(\)`) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 54 490 Td (  - Source: `invoices/models.py:Invoice.get_remaining_balance`) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 54 478 Td (  - Explanation: The remaining balance is the invoice total minus allocations already) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 54 466 Td (    applied.) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 54 454 Td (  - Example: Invoice amount = KES 12,000, amount paid = KES 5,000. Balance due = `12,000 -) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 54 442 Td (    5,000 = 7,000`.) Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 54 422 Td (Displayed field: Invoice Status) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 54 398 Td (  - Formula: `Paid if remaining <= 0; Partially Paid if remaining < invoice.amount;) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 54 386 Td (    otherwise Unpaid`) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 54 374 Td (  - Source: `invoices/models.py:Invoice.update_status`) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 54 362 Td (  - Explanation: Status follows the remaining balance.) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 54 350 Td (  - Example: Invoice amount = KES 12,000 and remaining = KES 0, status = `Paid`. If) Tj ET
