BT /F1 9 Tf 54 282 Td (    invoice.remaining_balance\)`) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 54 270 Td (  - Source: `invoices/views.py:attach_payment_to_invoice`) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 54 258 Td (  - Explanation: A payment cannot apply more credit than the payment has or more than the) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 54 246 Td (    invoice still needs.) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 54 234 Td (  - Example: Payment balance = KES 8,000 and invoice remaining balance = KES 5,000. Maximum) Tj ET
