BT /F1 9 Tf 54 638 Td (  - Source: `invoices/views.py:remove_invoice_payment`) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 54 626 Td (  - Explanation: Removing an allocation returns that amount to the payment as available) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 54 614 Td (    credit.) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 54 602 Td (  - Example: Removed allocation = KES 3,000 and payment balance was KES 1,000. New balance =) Tj ET
