BT /F2 10 Tf 54 570 Td (Displayed field: Automatic Rent Payment Allocation) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 54 546 Td (  - Formula: `amount_applied = min\(payment.balance, invoice.remaining_balance\)` applied to) Tj ET
