BT /F1 9 Tf 54 522 Td (  - Source: `invoices/services.py:allocate_payment_to_rent_invoices`) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 54 510 Td (  - Explanation: A rent payment is consumed against the oldest unpaid rent invoice until) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 54 498 Td (    either invoices are cleared or payment credit runs out.) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 54 486 Td (  - Example: Payment balance = KES 20,000. Oldest invoice needs KES 12,000 and next invoice) Tj ET
