BT /F2 10 Tf 54 442 Td (Displayed field: Existing Credit Applied To New Rent Invoice) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 54 418 Td (  - Formula: `amount_applied = min\(payment.balance, new_invoice.remaining_balance\)` for) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 54 406 Td (    tenant payments with credit.) Tj ET
