BT /F1 9 Tf 54 382 Td (  - Explanation: When a rent invoice is created, existing unallocated tenant credit can) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 54 370 Td (    automatically reduce it.) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 54 358 Td (  - Example: New invoice = KES 12,000 and tenant credit = KES 5,000. Applied credit =) Tj ET
